data.description: PRICED TO SELL!! Seller concessions for rate buy down/closing costs!! Stunning 2-story w/ covered entry ushering you into high ceilings, abundant natural light and neutral color palette. Chef's delight granite island kitchen w/ GAS COOKING!! Generous primary bedroom down  stairs w/ separate mud set shower, double vanities and large closet. Texas sized game room upstairs and plenty of space for everyone in the secondary bedrooms. Oversized covered patio and ample back yard for entertaining. Water softener, full sprinkler, radiant barrier roof! Great proximity and access to 1604 and minutes away from Lackland AFB!
